               Derivative Work;

         (ii)  Including the complete Source Code alongside the Object Code in
               every distribution, whether physical or electronic;

         (iii) Providing a written offer, valid for at least three (3) years
               and valid for as long as You offer spare parts or customer
               support for the Derivative Work, to give any third party a
               complete machine-readable copy of the corresponding Source Code,
               at no charge, via one of the methods described in (i) or (ii).

     (d) NETWORK USE COPYLEFT.  If You make the functionality of the Software
         or any Derivative Work available to third parties through Network Use,
         You must provide those third parties with access to the complete
         corresponding Source Code of the version they are interacting with,
