         of whether the Network Use constitutes Distribution under the laws of
         any particular jurisdiction.

         This provision is the functional equivalent of the "Affero clause"
         found in the GNU Affero General Public License, version 3 (AGPL-3.0),
         and is intended to close the "SaaS loophole" whereby modified versions
